❗️Parliament supported in the first reading the draft law on restarting the Bureau of Economic Security, - Chairman of the Committee on Finance, Tax and Customs Policy Danylo Hetmantsev. The updated draft bill took into account a number of proposals from business associations: - election of candidates for the position of the head of the BEB, with the majority vote of international experts ;
- immediate re-certification of all BEB employees;
